<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru" class="html">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, viewport-fit=cover, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="format-detection" content='telephone=no' />
	<meta name="format-detection" content='address=no' />
	<meta name="theme-color" content='#ffffff' />
	<!-- Ссылка на сайт -->
	<meta name="canonical" href="" />
	<meta name="description" content="{{ title }}" />
	<meta name="keywords" content="верстка, заказать верстку, сайт, разработка, HTML, CSS" />
	<meta name="Author" content="Николай Чёрный" />
	<meta name="Copyright" content="Николай Чёрный" />
	<meta name="Address" content="Украина, Киев" />
	<meta property="og:locale" content="ru_RU" />
	<meta property="og:type" content="article" />
	<meta property="og:site_name" content="grafit-off" />
	<meta property="og:title" content="GRAFIT-OFF - {{title}}" />
	<meta property="og:description" content=" {{title}}" />
	<meta property="og:image" content="{{img}}" />

	<!-- Favicons -->
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="57x57" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-57x57.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="60x60" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-60x60.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-72x72.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="76x76" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-76x76.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-114x114.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="120x120" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-120x120.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="144x144" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-144x144.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="152x152" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-152x152.png">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/apple-icon-180x180.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/android-icon-192x192.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/favicon-32x32.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="96x96" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/favicon-96x96.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/favicon-16x16.png">
	<link rel="manifest" href="../../assets/resources/favicons/manifest.json">
	<meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#ffffff">
	<meta name="msapplication-TileImage" content="../../assets/resources/favicons/ms-icon-144x144.png">

	<link rel="preload" href="../../assets/fonts/FuturaPT-Bold.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin />
	<link rel="preload" href="../../assets/fonts/FuturaPT-Book.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin />
	<link rel="preload" href="../../assets/fonts/FuturaPT-Medium.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin />

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../assets/css/paper.min.css" />
	<title>GRAFIT-OFF - {{ title }}</title>
</head>

<body class="body">
	<div class="wrap">
		{% include "header.njk" %}
		<main class="main-content">
			<section class="paper">
				<div class="paper__container container">
					<article class="paper__article article">
						<div class="article__promo">
							<div class="article__image">
								<img src="{{ img }}" alt="Обложка статьи" class="article__img">
							</div>
							<div class="article__info">
								<div class="article__time-info">
									<svg class="article__time-svg">
										<use xlink:href="../../assets/img/sprite.svg#clock"></use>
									</svg>
									<time class="article__time text-reset" datetime="2021-10-29 23:03">
										{{ time }}
									</time>
								</div>
								<h3 class="article__title text-reset">
									{{ title }}
								</h3>
							</div>
							<span class="article__tag">
								{{ tag }}
							</span>
						</div>
						<div class="article__content">
							{{ content | safe}}
						</div>
					</article>
					<aside class="paper__aside aside">
						<div class="aside__content">
							<h2 class="aside__title text-reset">
								Последние статьи:
							</h2>
							<ul class="aside__list list-reset">
								{% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
									{% if loop.index0 < 7 %}
										{% if title !== post.data.title %}
												<li class="aside__item aside-item">
													<div class="aside-item__article">
														<div class="aside-item__image">
															<img src="{{post.data.img}}" alt="Обложка статьи" class="aside-item__img">
														</div>
														<div class="aside-item__info">
															<div class="aside-item__time-info">
																<time class="aside-item__time text-reset" datetime="{{post.data.datetime}}">
																	{{post.data.time}}
																</time>
																<svg class="aside-item__time-svg">
																	<use xlink:href="../../assets/img/sprite.svg#clock"></use>
																</svg>
															</div>
															<h3 class="aside-item__title text-reset">
																{{post.data.title}}
															</h3>
														</div>
														<span class="aside-item__tag">
															{{post.data.tag}}
														</span>
														<a href="{{post.url}}" class="aside-item__link link-reset" aria-label="Перейти к статье"></a>
													</div>
												</li>
										{% endif %}
										{% if loop.length < 2 %}
												<li>
													Пусто
												</li>
											{% endif %}
									{% endif %}
								{% endfor %}
							</ul>
						</div>
					</aside>
					<div class="paper__author author-info">
						<div class="author-info__image">
							<svg class="author-info__svg">
								<use xlink:href="../../assets/img/sprite.svg#G-min"></use>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="author-info__content">
							<h3 class="author-info__heading text-reset">
								Об авторе
							</h3>
							<div class="author-info__name">
								Николай Чёрный
							</div>
							<p class="author-info__text text-reset">
								Привет! Я верстальщик, который специализируется на создании веб-сайтов разной сложности с использованием
								семантической и доступной разметки придерживаясь рекомендаций W3C и WAI-ARIA.
								Имею некоммерческий опыт разработки адаптивно-отзывчивых web-сайтов и готов выполнить ваш заказ в
								кратчайшие
								сроки с максимальным качеством!
							</p>
							<p class="author-info__text text-reset">
								Связатья со мной можно по ссылкам соц. сетей в навигации!
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		{% include "footer.njk" %}
	</div>	
	<script src="../../assets/js/main.js"></script>
	<script async src="../../assets/resources/libs/codepen.js"></script>
</body>

</html>